<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241675>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 8. Brueelia coryliventer n. sp. ex Creatophora cinerea. 7, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 8, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241675/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241676>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 12. Male genitalia, dorsal views. 9, Brueelia clara n. sp. 10, Brueelia rigbyi n. sp. 11, Brueelia tkachi n. sp. 12, Brueelia coryliventer n. sp. Abbreviations: lf = lateral fold; mf = median fold." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241676/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241677>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 16. Female subgenital plates and vulval margins, ventral views. 13, Brueelia clara n. sp. 14, Brueelia rigbyi n. sp. 15, Brueelia tkachi n. sp. 16, Brueelia coryliventer n. sp. Abbreviations: vms = vulval marginal setae; vos = vulval oblique setae; vss = vulval submarginal setae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241677/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241679>
    dc:description "FIGURES 19 – 20. Male heads, dorsal and ventral views. 19, Brueelia tkachi n. sp. 20, Brueelia coryliventer n. sp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241679/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241674>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 6. Brueelia tkachi n. sp. ex Spreo albicapillus albicapillus. 5, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 6, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241674/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

